)<GDSBplot>

The rightmost plot (@GDSBplot) tracks $alpha$ across iterations of the Gradient Descent using line search, illustrating
how the line search adapts the step size dynamically rather than relying on a
hand-tuned constant. The oscillatory behavior in $alpha$ is likely due to the Armijo-conditions being satisfied.




Lets compare the two convergences, and zoom in a bit

#figure(
